# .cursorrules — aiframework
# Stack: c / none
# Generated by aiframework. Run `aiframework refresh` to update.

## Commands

- Build: `make`
- Test: `make test`
- Lint: `cppcheck --enable=all .`
- Type check: `find . -name '*.sh' -not -path '*/.git/*' -not -path '*/vault/*' | xargs bash -n`
- Format: `clang-format -i`

## Conventions

- All heap allocations must have corresponding frees — verify with Valgrind or AddressSanitizer
- All user-facing buffers must use bounds-checked functions (snprintf, strncpy) — no strcpy/sprintf
- All public headers must use include guards or #pragma once
- Never commit secrets or credentials — use environment variables
- Run lint + test before committing

## Key Locations

- Source: `bin/`
- Source: `docs/`
- Source: `lib/`
- Source: `templates/`
- Source: `tests/`

